name: Flying Goodchilds
description:
• Tri-Blend (50% Polyester / 25% Cotton / 25% Rayon) T-shirt

The Flying Goodchilds were more than a sideshow act, they were a movement. A wave that swept the nation. They spoke of peace, prosperity, and the pike position. Sadly, the dream ended that chilly October night thanks to a haze of canadian whiskey and a mistimed timed swing by family patriarch Carl Goodchild. May we always remember the good times and the high times.

- last known picture Oct. 1965
